RACE.RACE_TEXT: DELTA DOWNS RACE 1 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 51. Maiden Claiming Purse 10000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Claiming Price $5,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: ASHLEY'S GIRL went to the front to lead throughout, edged away at the three eighths pole and drew clear proving much the best. BABY LOCKOUT broke in at the start then settled in the middle of the pack racing three to four wide and was no match for the winner. TENPINS TEMPEST was off a step slow then raced in the middle of the pack between rivals, made a bid on the final turn but didn't gain on the winner. MAYWON pressed the pace from the two path to the three eighths and weakened. JIVIN ASTRO was in the middle of the pack and not a factor. LUCKY CAJUN was five wide into the first turn then raced back around the final turn went five to six wide into upper stretch but was never a threat. MUCHO MACHO BABY was unsettled in the gate then tracked the leaders around the first turn then challenged the leaders at the seven sixteenths pole and stopped.
